RT by @sidhant: On 05.05.2026, an Indigo A321 aircraft operated flight 6E-108 (Hyderabad-Chandigarh). After landing, during taxi into the bay at Chandigarh, a power bank kept in a pouch in the seat pocket by a passenger seated on 39C caught fire. 

The aircraft was stopped in the bay. Cabin crew used two fire extinguisher bottles to extinguish the fire, then deployed all six slides to evacuate passengers. No passenger injuries have been reported.
@IndiGo6E #avgeeks
